<div class="headline"> 
  <h1>About The Prop Shop</h1>
</div>

<div class="about_intro">
  <div class="top_spacing row">
    <div class="span2">
      <%= image_tag("osrf_logo_only.png", alt:"OSRF Logo") %>
    </div>
  
    <div class="about_text span8 offset1">
      <p>The Prop Shop is brought to you by the <a href="http://osrfoundation.org" target="_blank">Open Source Robotics Foundation </a>(OSRF). The Prop Shop is a place for you to share your 3D models for use in simulation environments like <a href="http://gazebosim.org" target="_blank">Gazebo</a>. Share anything from a complex, high degree of freedom robot, to a model of a building, a tool, or a tree. By providing a database for freely-available 3D models, we hope to advance the state of robotic simulation by decreasing the barrier to entry for simulating a robot in a "realistic" simulation environment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

